    ResultsElement
    An abstract base class for types which represent test results.
    ResultsType
    The SystemResult is a container for one or more SystemResult instances.
    SystemType
    The SystemResult holds the evaluation results of the definitions and tests, as well as a copy of the OVAL System Characteristics used to perform the evaluation.
    TestedItemType
    The TestedItem holds a reference to a system characteristic item that matched the object specified in a test.
    TestedVariableType
    The TestedVariable holds the value to a variable used during the evaluation of a test.
    TestsType
    The TestResults is a container for one or more test instances.
    TestType
    The TestResult provides a reference to every item that matched the object section of the original test as well as providing an overall test result based on those items.
